## ✅ 9. Use Structured Data (Schema Markup)

Structured Data helps **rich results**.

Example:

```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "Improve SEO in React",
  "author": "Your Name"
}
```

✅ Boosts:

*   Featured snippets
*   FAQs
*   Rich cards

