## ✅ 10. Avoid SEO‑Killing React Mistakes

❌ Rendering everything client‑side\
❌ No `<h1>` per page\
❌ Same title on all routes\
❌ Blocking SEO content behind auth\
❌ Using `<div>` everywhere

***

## ✅ 11. Content Still Matters (A LOT)

React won’t save poor content.

✅ Best practices:

*   One topic per page
*   Clear headings (H1 → H2 → H3)
*   Match search intent
*   Avoid keyword stuffing

